{"TopicId":143869,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"Why is there a Monolith near KSC","CreatedByName":"Markus1002","CreatedById":155203,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-15T16:14:28Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Markus1002","CreatedById":155203,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-15T16:14:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI noticed that near space center, there is a monolith with Squad\u0027s logo. I think it has always been there. But for some reason when\u00A0I started the game, the monolith was visible from \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E, and I wasn\u0027t visible before. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:rolleyes:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_rolleyes.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:rolleyes:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Just Jim","CreatedById":148725,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-15T16:17:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn the last update they enlarged it considerably.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-07-15T16:19:16Z\u0022 title=\u002207/15/2016 04:19  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 15, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Just Jim\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-15T16:18:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYep. \u00A0It\u0027s always been there. \u00A0The 1.1.3 update made all of them bigger and fixed the easter eggs.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Van Disaster","CreatedById":58876,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-15T16:21:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs to why it\u0027s there... more likely \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E was built near a monolith.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Markus1002","CreatedById":155203,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-15T16:21:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOk, I just think that it should not be so visible, considering that it\u0027s an easter egg.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Van Disaster","CreatedById":58876,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-15T16:23:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222677335\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143869\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221468599678\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022155203\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Markus1002\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Markus1002 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOk, I just think that it should not be so visible, considering that it\u0027s an easter egg.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt makes players go \u0022ooh! I wonder if there\u0027s more...\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Markus1002","CreatedById":155203,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-15T16:24:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222677341\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143869\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221468599786\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002258876\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Van Disaster\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Van Disaster said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt makes players go \u0022ooh! I wonder if there\u0027s more...\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOk, it makes sense now.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Andem","CreatedById":155578,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-15T16:51:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222677335\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143869\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221468599678\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022155203\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Markus1002\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n25 minutes ago, Markus1002 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOk, I just think that it should not be so visible, considering that it\u0027s an easter egg.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n^^This!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis change has completely derailed the story I\u0027ve been setting up. Before the update, I made a conscious\u00A0decision to ignore the monoliths. Now, It\u0027s so stupidly massive that you can see it from anywhere on the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E peninsula. You can see it from the launch site, This change has COMPLETELY SCREWED ME OVER. I can basically just scrap the entire story now, as it hinges on the first and only anomaly being\u00A0Mun arches. Acknowledging easter eggs shouldn\u0027t be mandatory, the entire point is to stumble upon them accidentally or hunt them down, not have them shoved in your face.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"vger","CreatedById":67603,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-15T16:54:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe primitive Kerbals who touched it, beat problems (sometimes with skulls attached) with large femurs, which proved to be far more effective than the previous solution, which was yelling at problems until they either ran away or ate you. While the rest of the planet remained in the stone age, these advanced Kerbals continued developing technology around the monolith until they arrived at space travel.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Markus1002","CreatedById":155203,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-15T17:00:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222677387\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143869\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221468601697\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002267603\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022vger\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 minutes ago, vger said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe primitive Kerbals who touched it, beat problems (sometimes with skulls attached) with large femurs, which proved to be far more effective than the previous solution, which was yelling at problems until they either ran away or ate you. While the rest of the planet remained in the stone age, these advanced Kerbals continued developing technology around the monolith until they arrived at space travel.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI never thought of that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Randazzo","CreatedById":136468,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-15T17:06:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222677394\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143869\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221468602044\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022155203\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Markus1002\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 minutes ago, Markus1002 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI never thought of that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nlol\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n/thread\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Andem","CreatedById":155578,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-15T17:17:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222677408\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143869\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221468602429\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022101028\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022WildLynx\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, WildLynx said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://xkcd.com/1172/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://xkcd.com/1172/\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s\u00A0a completely different situation. That comic involves a hardware problem, whle this is just, quite frankly, stupid. An easter egg is described as:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cu\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:rgb(34,34,34);font-family:arial, \u0027sans-serif-light\u0027, sans-serif;font-size:small;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:100;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:normal;text-align:left;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;float:none;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\u0022\u003EEaster Egg - An \u003Cem\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003Eunexpected \u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/em\u003Eor undocumented feature in a piece of computer software or on a DVD, included as a \u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cem\u003Ejoke or a bonus\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/u\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:rgb(34,34,34);font-family:arial, \u0027sans-serif-light\u0027, sans-serif;font-size:small;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:100;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:normal;text-align:left;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;float:none;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\u0022\u003EThat is what the monoliths are. Instead, they\u0027re getting shoved down your throat FOR NO REASON AT ALL! IT\u0027S NOT LIKE THEY\u0027RE IMPERATIVE TO THE GAME\u0027S FUNCTION, THEY ARE A BONUS. Why did none of the other monoliths get 10 times the size? Why not JUST LEAVE IT THE SAME GODDAMN SIZE!!!\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:rgb(34,34,34);font-family:arial, \u0027sans-serif-light\u0027, sans-serif;font-size:small;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:100;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:normal;text-align:left;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;float:none;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\u0022\u003ESeriously, This is like, a months worth of carefull planning and writing that has been completely wasted. And I can\u0027t roll back to 1.1.2 now, or I already would have.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"vger","CreatedById":67603,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-15T17:19:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222677425\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143869\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221468603049\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022155578\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Andem\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Andem said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:rgb(34,34,34);font-family:arial, \u0027sans-serif-light\u0027, sans-serif;font-size:small;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:100;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:normal;text-align:left;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;float:none;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\u0022\u003EWhy did none of the other monoliths get 10 times the size?\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBecause none of the other monoliths ordered the pills that were advertised to them in their email.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Andem","CreatedById":155578,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-15T18:01:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222677442\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143869\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221468603399\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022101028\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022WildLynx\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n37 minutes ago, WildLynx said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI use SCANSat, so no location-bound Easter Eggs are hidden from me. Uh, I\u0027m so sure?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t use Scansat. I used too, but there were other mod conflicts and I chose to just drop it. I\u0027m unsure why that mod has any bearing on this discussion whatsoever.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rocket In My Pocket","CreatedById":154640,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-15T18:07:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is KSP, we solve our problems via engineering.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you don\u0027t like the monolith being there, Build a frigging\u00A0wall on wheels and drive it over there in front of it so you don\u0027t have to see it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr even park a rocket ship there; call it a\u00A0memorial, build a statue of the first Kerbal astronaut, some kind of fake \u0022building\u0022...I don\u0027t know...anything!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-07-15T18:07:56Z\u0022 title=\u002207/15/2016 06:07  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 15, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Rocket In My Pocket\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GarrisonChisholm","CreatedById":146403,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-15T18:08:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222677387\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143869\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221468601697\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002267603\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022vger\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, vger said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n... yelling at problems until they either ran away or ate you.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHuh, ... my office operates this way...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Trann","CreatedById":83801,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-15T18:15:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n...write a mod to rescale Monoliths?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Andem","CreatedById":155578,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-15T18:25:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222677503\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143869\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221468606052\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154640\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Rocket In My Pocket\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n16 minutes ago, Rocket In My Pocket said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is KSP, we solve our problems via engineering.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you don\u0027t like the monolith being there, Build a frigging\u00A0wall on wheels and drive it over there in front of it so you don\u0027t have to see it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr even park a rocket ship there; call it a\u00A0memorial, build a statue of the first Kerbal astronaut, some kind of fake \u0022building\u0022...I don\u0027t know...anything!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot possible. Career mate.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222677517\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143869\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221468606518\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002283801\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Trann\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n9 minutes ago, Trann said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n...write a mod to rescale Monoliths?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI doubt that that\u0027s even possible, but if it was, I don\u0027t have the skills to do so.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rocket In My Pocket","CreatedById":154640,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-15T19:10:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222677545\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143869\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221468607136\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022155578\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Andem\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n43 minutes ago, Andem said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot possible. Career mate.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI play Career too.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn what way is it not possible?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBuild a wall, put wheels on it, launch it, drive it over there, return to space center, done.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"razark","CreatedById":32993,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-15T19:18:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222677382\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143869\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221468601508\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022155578\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Andem\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Andem said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis change has completely derailed the story I\u0027ve been setting up.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhy not just ignore it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Andem","CreatedById":155578,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-15T19:21:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222677638\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143869\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221468610303\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002232993\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022razark\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, razark said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhy not just ignore it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSee:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222677382\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143869\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221468601508\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022155578\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Andem\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Andem said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNow, It\u0027s so stupidly massive that you can see it from anywhere on the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E peninsula. You can see it from the launch site.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s so massive and garish that you can\u0027t not see it. And, In my opinion, it\u0027s an eyesore. Especially if the story includes some anomalies but not the others, it would just be weird.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n--EDIT--\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI just remembered, I can \u0022Kopernicusify\u0022 the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E to a new location! I can\u0027t believe it took me so long to remember that... Crisis (hypothetically) avoided I guess... But I would still appreciate this changed back to a normal size.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:confused:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_huh.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:confused:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-07-15T19:23:25Z\u0022 title=\u002207/15/2016 07:23  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 15, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Andem\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"razark","CreatedById":32993,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-15T19:29:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222677646\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143869\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221468610488\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022155578\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Andem\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Andem said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s so massive and garish that you can\u0027t not see it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes.\u00A0 I get that point.\u00A0 But just because you \u003Cem\u003Ecan\u003C/em\u003E see it doesn\u0027t mean you \u003Cem\u003Ehave\u003C/em\u003E to.\u00A0 Or that you have to accept it as an out-of-place artifact.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222677646\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143869\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221468610488\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022155578\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Andem\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Andem said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n...if the story includes some anomalies but not the others...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat anomaly?\u00A0 It\u0027s just part of the landscape in the background, and you don\u0027t even need to really acknowledge that it exists in the first place.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nor:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0022Hey, what\u0027s the thing?\u0022\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u0022Oh, you mean that historical monument over there?\u00A0 Yeah, some people aren\u0027t happy with it, but it\u0027s really not important to what we do over here, so we just don\u0027t really talk about it.\u0022\u003Cbr\u003E\nStory continues from this point without ever acknowledging the monolith\u0027s existence ever again.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Brownhair2","CreatedById":128730,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-15T19:44:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222677425\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143869\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221468603049\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022155578\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Andem\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Andem said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:rgb(34,34,34);font-family:arial, \u0027sans-serif-light\u0027, sans-serif;font-size:small;line-height:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\u0022\u003EWhy did none of the other monoliths get 10 times the size?\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey did.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Just Jim","CreatedById":148725,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-15T19:57:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222677681\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143869\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221468611873\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022128730\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Brownhair2\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n13 minutes ago, Brownhair2 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey did.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAll the ones I\u0027ve looked at have grown.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222677646\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143869\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221468610488\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022155578\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Andem\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n36 minutes ago, Andem said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s so massive and garish that you can\u0027t not see it. And, In my opinion, it\u0027s an eyesore. Especially if the story includes some anomalies but not the others, it would just be weird.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n--EDIT--\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI just remembered, I can \u0022Kopernicusify\u0022 the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E to a new location! I can\u0027t believe it took me so long to remember that... Crisis (hypothetically) avoided I guess... But I would still appreciate this changed back to a normal size.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:confused:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_huh.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:confused:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s getting a little off-topic, but I\u0027ve been thinking of different excuses for future changes like this.\u00A0 Luckily Emiko Station is a little weird already, so unexplained giant monoliths was fairly easy to write in.\u00A0 But still, I\u0027ve been trying to think of different ideas to explain any other changes that might pop up in future updates, just in case.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-07-15T19:58:04Z\u0022 title=\u002207/15/2016 07:58  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 15, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Just Jim\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"vger","CreatedById":67603,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-15T20:02:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222677517\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143869\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221468606518\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002283801\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Trann\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Trann said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n...write a mod to rescale Monoliths?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr make them destructible. Fly a dummy rocket into it. Problem solved.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nThough, maybe they already are and nobody bothered to try crashing into one?\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nMaking it possible to grapple them with the claw is another option. There\u0027d be a fun diversionary metagame. Collect every monolith in the solar system. When they are all parked on the same planet within a certain range of each other, the space baby shows up in orbit. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-07-15T20:04:32Z\u0022 title=\u002207/15/2016 08:04  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 15, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by vger\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}